{
  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 195832,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「魔王ランスと直接対峙した者は少ないから……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"There are few who have faced the Demon King Rance directly...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195833,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　特に＜エール＞は知らないだろうけど」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Especially, 'Aile' probably doesn't know."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195834,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「僕は昔の父上がどんな人だったかは知らないが、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I don't know what my old father was like,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195835,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　魔王ランスがどんな人物だったかは知っている」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "but I know what kind of person Demon King Rance was.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195836,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……どんな奴なん？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...What kind of guy was he?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195837,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……理性の消え失せた化け物」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...A monster who lost all reason.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195838,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "それは、乱義の言葉とは思えない",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "That was not a word one would expect from Rangy."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195839,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "乱暴な評価だった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "It was a harsh evaluation."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195840,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「男は殺す、女は犯す。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"He kills men, and violates women."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195841,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　刃向かうものは男女と年齢の別なく殺す」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "He kills anyone who resists, regardless of gender or age.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195842,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「今も空に浮いている旧ランス城、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"The old Rance Castle still floating in the sky,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195843,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　鬼畜王戦争時あの城を拠点として人類は結束」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "was the base during the Fiend King War where humanity united.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195844,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「みんなも会ったミラクルさん、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Miracle-san, whom everyone has met,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195845,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　彼女を中心としてカオスオーナーカーマさん、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "around her gathered Chaos Owner Karma-san,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195846,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　パットンさん、アレキサンダーさんも集結した」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "as well as Patton-san and Alexander-san.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195847,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「す、すげぇ、まるでオールスターだな」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"A-Amazing, it's like an all-star lineup.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195848,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はんっ、そんだけ集まって",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmph, even with all of them gathered"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195849,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　手も足も出なかったってよ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "they couldn't do a thing.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195850,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ええっ、嘘だろ？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"What? No way.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195851,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……事実よ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...It's true.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195852,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はっはっはっ、それくらい",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ha ha ha, that much"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195853,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　魔王ランスは凄まじい強さだったということだ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "shows how incredibly strong Demon King Rance was.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195854,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「魔人は工夫と結束、それでどうにか退けてもな、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"The demons might fend him off with ingenuity and unity,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195855,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　奥に控える魔王には誰も太刀打ちできなかった」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "but none could stand against the Demon King lurking behind.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195856,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"........\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195857,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "当時のことを思い出しているのか、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "As if recalling those times,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195858,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "乱義の表情が深く沈む。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Rangy's expression grew deeply somber."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195859,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「本当に……あれは奇跡だった」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Truly... that was a miracle.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195860,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ごくごく一瞬の間に湧いた隙、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"An opening that appeared in just an instant,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195861,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　そこにリセットのビンタがバチン」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and Reset's slap landed with a smack right there.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195862,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ふふ、同じことをもう一度同じメンバーでやれ、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Heh heh, even if we were told to do the same thing again with the same members,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195863,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　と、言われてももうごめんだな」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I'd say no thanks now.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195864,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ふんっ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmph.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195865,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ザンスは鼻を鳴らした。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Zansu snorted."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195866,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「魔王ランスってなぁ、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Demon King Rance, you see,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195867,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　五年周期で魔王としての血に覚醒する。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "wakes up the blood of a Demon King in five-year cycles."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195868,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　凶暴になり理性を失い人を襲う」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "He becomes violent, loses reason, and attacks people.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195869,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「五年周期ってことは……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Five-year cycle means...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195870,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「おお、そろそろ暴れ出すだろうぜ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yeah, he's probably about to start rampaging."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195871,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　つまり――」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "In other words—\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195872,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「今が最後のチャンスだろーな」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Now is the last chance, right?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195873,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「今なら、まだ油断もあんだろう。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Right now, he might still be careless."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195874,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　敵意も薄い可能性もある」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "There might even be a lack of hostile intent.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195875,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「やるなら、今だ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"If we're going to do it, it's now.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195876,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それは、まあ……そうだけど……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Well, that's... true, but...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195877,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ああ、そうだね……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yeah, that's right...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195878,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ザンスの言葉を引き継ぎ、乱義が頷く。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Taking over Zansu's words, Rangy nodded."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195879,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「強い敵と戦いたくないというのも、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Not wanting to fight a strong enemy,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195880,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　家族を失いたくないと考えるのも自然だ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and not wanting to lose family is natural.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195881,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「でもね……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"But you know...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195882,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「そろそろ覚悟を決める必要はあると思う」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I think it's time to make up our minds.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195883,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あ、うっ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah, uh...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195884,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「うん、そうだよね……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yeah, that's right...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195885,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「これ以上うだうだすんのは",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Dragging this out any longer"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195886,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　俺の趣味じゃねーから文句ある奴はしばく」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "is not my style, so anyone with complaints will get smacked.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195887,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ええっ！　しばくの！？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"What!? You're going to smack them!?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195888,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"........\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195889,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「今回は珍しく……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"This time, unusually..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195890,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ザンスの言うことが正論ね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Zansu's words are the correct ones.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195891,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「アア？　珍しくだぁ？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Huh? Unusually, huh?\""
    }
  ]
}

